# Deployment — tv.bakeandgrill.mv

After every `git push`, always provide the cPanel pull & deploy instructions:

## After Every Push

The `client/dist/` folder is pre-built locally and committed to the repo.
**NEVER run `npm run build` on the cPanel server** — vite is not installed there.

### Full deploy command (cPanel server)
```bash
cd ~/tv.bakeandgrill.mv && \
  GIT_SSH_COMMAND="ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_ed25519 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes" git pull origin main
```

Then: **cPanel → Setup Node.js App → RESTART** (click the restart button)

### Verify
```bash
curl https://tv.bakeandgrill.mv/api/health
```

